	<h1 class="title">视频都会变成竖着的，这不是什么坏事</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
				<span class="name">Farhad Manjoo</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-08-14 11:55:36 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/13516/medium/13516.jpg?1439517120" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


